    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">
          <i class="fa fa-pencil" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Creating a pdf file
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">

        <p>
          To allow a
          <strong>long-term preservation</strong>
          of your publication, please consider the following by creating your pdf file:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            All used
            <strong>fonts and images</strong>
            must be integrated into the file.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>No encryption or password protection</strong>
            , not even for parts of your work, like printing or copying.
          </li>
          <li>
            Please assure that a
            <strong>full-text search</strong>
            is possible in your file.
          </li>
          <li>
            Create your file in the
            <a href="http://www.pdfa.org/" target="_blank">PDF/A</a>
            format whenever possible.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <di>
